TITLE: Message Handling Using OnInsert Callback in SpacetimeDB C#
DESCRIPTION: Defines a `Message.OnInsert` callback function for printing new messages received by a user in SpacetimeDB. It checks the context to ensure only new messages are printed and uses a helper function `PrintMessage` to display the message details.
