DESCRIPTION: This code defines the FoodController class, which inherits from EntityController. It handles spawning and management of food game objects, including color assignment based on entity ID.
SOURCE: https://github.com/clockworklabs/spacetime-docs/blob/master/docs/unity/part-3.md#2025-04-18_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: cs
