TITLE: SpacetimeDB C Bindings Header
DESCRIPTION: C header file defining the interface between WASM modules and SpacetimeDB, including buffer management, logging, scheduling, and table operations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/clockworklabs/spacetime-docs/blob/master/docs/webassembly-abi/index.md#2025-04-18_snippet_8

